name: 5.56 ETC speedloader
description: This speedloader can hold 4 rounds of 5.56mm ETC and quickly reload a compatible revolver.

name: OCM5-14 standard magazine
description: A compact 14-round 5.56 ETC magazine compatible with OmniCorp guns. Almost STANAG-compatible, an internal mechanism that only fits in with plasma primers prevent erroneous loading.
